Slippery Slope

An honest life according to the laws of other people is not suitable for everyone. Why live that way when you can make your own laws? If you feel close to these words, this is the right path for you. Play as a resident of a poor neighbourhood for whom the law is the street.

Make friends with the crime bosses, start at the bottom and work your way to the top of the underworld, run your own gang and keep areas under your control.

The American Dream

Do you have respect for honest work and want to achieve everything yourself? Then the American dream is for you. Get a good job and lead your own life. Work made a man out of a monkey, don't forget that.

So if you are willing to face life's challenges and pursue your dreams by obeying the law, then you can rise to the top of government or other state structures.
